<h2 style="color: #CC0000">Lilac Hotel</h2>    
  Located in Bangalore, Lilac Hotel, 3rd Block offers comfortable accommodation and a fitness centre. The hotel features free WiFi. The property is 2.8 km from Lalbaug and 600 m from the metro station

The accommodation will provide you with air conditioning and a seating area. There is a full a kitchenette with a microwave and a refrigerator. Featuring a shower, private bathroom also comes with a hairdryer and free toiletries.

At Lilac Hotel, 3rd Block you will find a 24-hour front desk. Other facilities like a shared lounge are offered. The property offers free parking.

It is 5.8 km from Cubbon Park and 12.1 km from Iskcon Temple. The Majestic Railway Station is 6.9 km away and the Kempegowda International Airport is located 39 km from the property.

<h2 style="color: #CC0000">The Tamara Coorg </h2>
The Tamara Coorg is a 5-star property about 8 km from Nalkanad Palace and Thadiandamol. Featuring contemporary resort-style decor, all guestrooms come with a private terrace where guests can enjoy fresh mountain air and watch birds. Free WiFi is available throughout the property.

Spacious and air-conditioned, all rooms and suites include a flat-screen TV, sofa and minibar. The en suite bathrooms are equipped with shower facility.

The Tamara Coorg is 12 km from Iguthappa Temple and 27 km from Viraipet. It is 42 km from Talacauvery. Madikeri is 38 km away. Free parking is available.

The Falls offers multi-cuisine delights to the guests, while freshly brewed coffee can be enjoyed at The Verandah. Cocktails are available at The Deck bar.

Guests can arrange day trips at the tour desk, or make use of the meeting rooms. The front desk operates 24 hours.

<h2 style="color: #CC0000"> Hotel MB International Palace</h2>
Situated 500 m from Mysore Palace and the nearest bus station, Hotel MB International Palace Side features a restaurant, disability friendly facilities and free private parking.

The hotel is 1 km from Mysore Zoo and St. Philomena's Church. Mysore Railway Station is 3 km away, while Mysore Airport is 10 km away.

Rooms are air-conditioned, and feature a flat-screen TV, a wardrobe, an electric kettle and a minibar. The en suite bathroom comes with shower facilities, toiletries and a hairdryer.

Spices Sauces serves Indian, Chinese and Continental delights and offers the daily buffet breakfast. Room service is provided.

The 24-hour front desk staff can assist with laundry, luggage storage and car rental services. Travel arrangements can be made at the tour desk.

This is our guests' favourite part of Mysore, according to independent reviews.

<h2 style="color: #CC0000">Koomankolly Resort</h2>
Set in Thirunelli, KOOMANKOLLY RESORT features a garden. Boasting a 24-hour front desk, this property also provides guests with a restaurant. The accommodation offers room service, and organising tours for guests.

Featuring a private bathroom with a shower and free toiletries, certain rooms at the resort also boast a mountain view.

An Asian breakfast is served every morning at the property.

The area is popular for safari tours and car hire is available at KOOMANKOLLY RESORT. Wildlife Safari at Nagarhole national park can be arranged.

The nearest airport is Kannur International Airport, 87 km from the property
 
